This paper discusses a logging tool for Android devices that can be used in various research fields such as user authentication, intrusion detection, and detection of information leaks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security), followed by cs.SY (Systems and Control), cs.SE (Software Engineering), cs.HC (Human-Computer Interaction), and cs.CY (Computers and Society).
